{"type":"article_comment","id":310873,"parentType":"article","parentId":16625,"uid":21875,"contents":"<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/item_id-310485#answer_list_310485\"><blockquote>联想到郭沫若大神。四海《通知》遍，文革卷风云，阶级斗争纲举，打倒刘和林。十载春风化雨，喜见山花烂漫，...</blockquote></a><br>\n所以才有遠看是條狗，近看郭沫若一說。","date":"2020-03-22","agreeCount":0,"discussionCount":0}